{"tid":2159505,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"自民黨高層：日本不應忽視 TikTok 數據安全風險　最快 9 月提案促限制使用","createTime":"2020-08-16T11:08:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T11:08:04.000Z","uid":75656,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"63523fbae9d7e1f7e93fd8a859641750b294fea5","tid":2159505,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T11:08:04.000Z","msg":"甘利明當地時間今日（16 日）接受富士電視台訪問時指，其他國家包括英國、印度、美國等均已指出 TikTok 可能存在的數據安全風險，日本不應忽視，「已經有太多國家指出了這風險，日本不能袖手旁觀。」<br />\n<br />\n甘利明在 7 月時曾表示，美國正積極敦促其他國家考慮與中國應用程式有關的數據風險，自民黨的相關委員會將展開調查，並評估其對國家安全的影響。上月底時，多名日本議員表明考慮促請政府對中國應用程式施加限制，原因是擔心用戶數據可能落入中國政府手中，甘利明當時指，將促請政府採取立法措施，限制使用  TikTok 等中國應用程式，最快在 9 月向政府提交議案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E8%87%AA%E6%B0%91%E9%BB%A8%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E5%BF%BD%E8%A6%96-tiktok-%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB-9-%E6%9C%88%E6%8F%90%E6%A1%88%E4%BF%83%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B1%25A4-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25BF%25BD%25E8%25A6%2596-tiktok-%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%259A%25AA-%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BF%25AB-9-%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%258F%2590%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25BF%2583%25E9%2599%2590%25E5%2588%25B6%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJMZiPQ%2BZ2BAZCV%2B6nVsqWzo%3D&h=9f5b6a6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B1%25A4-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25BF%25BD%25E8%25A6%2596-tiktok-%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%259A%25AA-%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BF%25AB-9-%25E6%259C%258